description: A company that truly cares, Ibison Concessions & Catering brings over 20 years of experience in festival fun straight to everyone throughout Vicksburg with their premium assortment of carnival cuisine. Made-from-scratch Elephant Ears, Hot Soft Pretzels, Sundaes, Floats, Burgers, Pizza, Subs, all your favorite kinds of fries...For all this and much more, call on Ibison Concessions & Catering to come make your next event unforgettable as your guests dive right into this whimsical deliciousness!
name: Ibison Concessions &  Catering
